      "text": [
        " : «إِنَّ اَللَّهَ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ اِخْتَارَ مِنْ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ شَيْئاً وَ اِخْتَارَ مِنَ اَلْأَرْضِ مَوْضِعَ اَلْكَعْبَةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2306 - It has been narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) that he said:\n\"Indeed, Allah (swt), the Mighty and Majestic, chose something special from everything, and He chose from the earth the location of the Kaaba.\""
        ]
